- Yeah.
- Nose piercing?

261
00:14:55,434 --> 00:14:57,864
- Yeah!
- So? What's Yasu doing now?

262
00:14:58,004 --> 00:15:00,264
I mean it, shut up, Naoki.

263
00:15:00,434 --> 00:15:02,494
I haven't had much sleep.
Let me sleep.

264
00:15:02,704 --> 00:15:03,874
Someone switch seats with him.

265
00:15:03,874 --> 00:15:06,404
Then I'll switch with Naoki.

266
00:15:09,344 --> 00:15:13,184
Hey, Take, which side is Mount Fuji?
Which side can we see it from?

267
00:15:13,354 --> 00:15:14,444
Are you listening?

268
00:15:15,684 --> 00:15:17,584
- Say, Takumi...
- Yasu?

269
00:15:18,024 --> 00:15:19,514
